Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.61,0:00:11.32,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在在你眼前 有着无限的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.29,0:00:17.96,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,照亮了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.03,0:00:21.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs38\pos(450,390)\1c&HFFFFFF&}海底两万里 / {\fs18}蓝宝石之谜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.04,0:00:30.10,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讨厌懦弱的人 无法背叛蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.18,0:00:36.45,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在做梦之前 我想翱翔天际
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.28,0:00:44.19,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,心中的音乐盒开启 发出声响
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.26,0:00:51.43,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一点一滴演奏出幸福与勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.50,0:01:00.20,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在在你眼前 有着无限的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.27,0:01:05.64,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,言语是永远的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.71,0:01:10.55,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't forget to try in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.62,0:01:15.55,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爱比宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.39,0:01:22.76,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,更能照亮一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.04,0:01:41.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,时值公元1889年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.41,0:01:45.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在巴黎万国博览会上认识的 强、娜蒂亚以及大王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.18,0:01:49.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,遭到企图夺取神秘宝石 『蔚蓝之水』的邪恶三人组袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.79,0:01:53.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,藉由强所发明的飞机 好不容易逃离险境
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.76,0:01:57.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,经历多次冒险 他们迫降于某座岛屿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.56,0:02:02.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没想到那里竟是神秘组织 『新亚特兰提斯』 的秘密基地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.37,0:02:06.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强他们在那座岛上 认识了小女孩玛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.34,0:02:10.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但娜蒂亚他们却被 带着面具的男子石像鬼捉走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.38,0:02:13.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还被迫参观杀人兵器 『巴别塔』的实验
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.21,0:02:17.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其威力竟足以摧毁海上小岛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.15,0:02:22.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所幸强与三人组大显身手 平安将娜蒂亚他们救出
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.69,0:02:26.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,秘密基地也由于 万能潜水艇鹦鹉螺号的活跃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.59,0:02:28.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因而毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.50,0:02:32.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,后来强等人搭上鹦鹉螺号
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.07,0:02:35.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,葛兰迪丝对尼莫一见钟情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.00,0:02:38.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫与娜蒂亚 则是在命运的安排下重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.47,0:02:42.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原来尼莫也是蔚蓝之水的继承人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.48,0:02:47.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一行人在鹦鹉螺号舰内 展开新的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.41,0:02:50.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强他们虽然尚无法习惯 潜水艇内的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.32,0:02:52.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,却还是坚强地活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.79,0:02:55.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,经历了新亚特兰提斯的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.32,0:02:56.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,众人的离合
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.02,0:03:01.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以及大自然的惊奇等 超乎想像的苦难航程后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.33,0:03:05.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鹦鹉螺号终于面临 与石像鬼的空中战舰对峙的局面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.87,0:03:08.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是在敌人压倒性的武力面前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.57,0:03:11.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鹦鹉螺号毫无招架之力 遭到击沉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.07,0:03:15.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在逐渐沉没至深海的 鹦鹉螺号中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.31,0:03:19.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚得知尼莫就是 毁灭自己故乡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.58,0:03:21.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因而大受打击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.45,0:03:27.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫背负着必须消灭石像鬼 与新亚特兰提斯的沉重十字架
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.15,0:03:30.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而后来娜蒂亚才得知
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.46,0:03:32.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫竟是她的父亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.49,0:03:37.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但那时娜蒂亚他们 所乘坐的救生舱已经分离
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.20,0:03:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫等人所在的主船舱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.13,0:03:42.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,则消失在黑暗的深海之中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.57,0:03:43.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,『活下去』
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.54,0:03:45.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫留给了娜蒂亚这句话…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.07,0:03:47.87,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,#23 小小漂流者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.22,0:04:06.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们两个是怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.16,0:04:08.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,桑森跟韩森呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.13,0:04:12.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家都去哪里了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.47,0:04:20.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你为什么在哭？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.85,0:04:31.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要去找大家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.95,0:04:35.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行 玛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.79,0:04:37.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.26,0:04:39.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,门的另一边…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.23,0:04:41.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.73,0:04:44.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,门的另一边没有任何人在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.41,0:04:56.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好无聊喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.61,0:05:01.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王 来玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.78,0:05:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好想玩 好想玩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.29,0:05:13.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跟大王一起玩…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.03,0:05:22.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跟桑森一起玩…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.35,0:05:36.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们究竟正往哪里去呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.32,0:05:41.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.27,0:05:53.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.34,0:06:01.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请做出裁示吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.44,0:06:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,直到你女儿 娜蒂亚出现在你面前为止
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.01,0:06:09.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你为什么要恢复成 一名普通的父亲呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.02,0:06:13.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么不继续当那个 我深爱的男子直到最后呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.55,0:06:15.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再见了 尼莫船长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.59,0:06:18.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,住手 请你住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.16,0:06:19.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.39,0:06:21.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,求求你 请你不要开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.70,0:06:24.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.60,0:06:28.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我记得『尼莫』在拉丁文里 代表着『什么人都不是』的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.10,0:06:32.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不喜欢这艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.31,0:06:34.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,来得正好 我来介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.54,0:06:36.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这位是娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.98,0:06:38.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是真正的海上男儿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.21,0:06:41.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚 你不那么认为吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.72,0:06:45.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,老是抱著书在啃的你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.89,0:06:49.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还是觉得待在天空之下 比窝在科学精华里来得好是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.92,0:06:52.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为尼莫船长人那么好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.23,0:06:55.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我话似乎多了点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.19,0:06:57.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那位先生正是海中宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.23,0:06:59.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,男人中的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.57,0:07:01.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.60,0:07:02.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么要开枪？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.04,0:07:05.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个人明明已经受伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.44,0:07:08.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,被子弹射中的人 可能是你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.44,0:07:09.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,杀人凶手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.48,0:07:11.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你根本就不是人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.61,0:07:14.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跟现在的你解释 也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.91,0:07:17.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好狡猾 你想逃避是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.22,0:07:24.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.82,0:07:27.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别说出那么伤人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.10,0:07:34.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好想玩 好想玩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.23,0:07:39.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好想跟娜蒂亚一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.31,0:07:46.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚 你看看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.21,0:07:51.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好棒喔 这是百科全书
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.38,0:07:53.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,里头记载了世界上的所有事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.82,0:07:59.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你看 光哲学、宗教、文学 医学、历史就各占了三册
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.19,0:08:01.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,物理、化学、地球、宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.49,0:08:04.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还有人名辞典 与世界地图的附录
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.70,0:08:07.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要有这个就无所不知了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.33,0:08:10.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那你告诉我 我们接下来会怎样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.14,0:08:13.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们被关在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.04,0:08:17.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没有目的地 说不定会沉入海里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.24,0:08:21.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且石像鬼 可能在海面上等着我们耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.48,0:08:23.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那些书里什么都有写不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.92,0:08:25.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你告诉我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.35,0:08:27.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没…没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.35,0:08:28.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为有浮力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.55,0:08:30.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们随时都能浮出海面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.69,0:08:33.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这里也囤积了不少紧急粮食
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.49,0:08:36.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再说这个房间 是由宇宙钛金所构成
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.73,0:08:38.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一些小碰撞是不会构成威胁的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.07,0:08:41.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这艘船曾经遭到严重攻击耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.10,0:08:44.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算现在破了洞进水也不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.51,0:08:48.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看吧 就跟我说的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.14,0:08:50.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不…不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.72,0:09:02.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看来这个房间也损伤得不轻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.96,0:09:07.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要是轻微的冲撞 或许又会再漏水
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.16,0:09:10.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家要尽量保持安静 尽可能不要移动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.70,0:09:11.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.46,0:09:12.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.91,0:09:26.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还不行动吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.05,0:09:28.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还不行\N还不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.66,0:09:43.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好想玩 好想玩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.68,0:10:04.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我好像感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.30,0:10:19.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以才说科学一点都不可信嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.13,0:10:20.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 你这个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.73,0:10:23.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果你是男人 就快想点办法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.07,0:10:25.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 我好歹是个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.65,0:10:38.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 你好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.25,0:10:39.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我对你刮目相看了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.55,0:10:43.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小…小事一桩…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.59,0:10:49.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.21,0:11:00.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,各位 很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.57,0:11:04.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都是…都是因为我打了喷嚏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.52,0:11:11.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们会就这样淹死是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.05,0:11:14.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 打开这个气阀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.36,0:11:19.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一打开这个气阀 水就会跑进来耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.83,0:11:22.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那种事就连玛莉与大王也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.56,0:11:24.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.26,0:11:29.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,水会跑进来就表示 同时会有空气跑出去对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.97,0:11:30.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然后呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.00,0:11:32.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这就对啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.04,0:11:35.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,空气的比重比水轻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.44,0:11:37.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它会朝着海面浮上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.08,0:11:40.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要将空气收集在这把伞里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.51,0:11:42.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再把头伸进去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.58,0:11:43.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算水跑进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.48,0:11:45.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,伞中的空气依旧存在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.68,0:11:47.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们还是能继续呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.15,0:11:49.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然后我们也会 跟着空气一起上升
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.49,0:11:52.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样就能顺利浮出海面了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.36,0:11:53.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.69,0:11:55.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很棒的主意吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.46,0:11:56.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你太厉害了 强
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.00,0:11:58.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这真是个好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.56,0:12:00.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,死里求生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.43,0:12:02.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,艾丽朵拉也常那么说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.84,0:12:05.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.48,0:12:13.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要开始啰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.68,0:12:19.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一 二 三…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.69,0:12:54.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,得救了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.59,0:12:57.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.32,0:13:00.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看来我是白担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.48,0:13:24.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.39,0:13:29.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这里是哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.26,0:13:39.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,会是非洲吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.73,0:13:45.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 我记得非洲应该没有 这种品种的椰子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.57,0:13:48.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.29,0:14:05.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王 不可以弄垮啦 你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.82,0:14:07.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真羡慕小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.83,0:14:11.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在说什么啊 你不也还是小孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.90,0:14:13.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,又要讨论这个话题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.07,0:14:17.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那你不也一样是小孩子吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.94,0:14:22.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我根本没时间当小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.51,0:14:25.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.65,0:14:29.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对不起 你也一样对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.05,0:14:32.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.49,0:14:35.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这里也许会有城市或村庄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.62,0:14:36.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.36,0:14:37.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.92,0:14:40.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你看 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.26,0:14:43.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我捡到这个喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.30,0:14:46.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,掉了好多喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.00,0:14:50.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是石像鬼的罐头
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.20,0:14:52.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是在哪边捡到的？玛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.07,0:14:53.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.34,0:14:54.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.61,0:14:56.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这里也有石像鬼的基地吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.98,0:14:58.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,先调查看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.88,0:15:00.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.42,0:15:07.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,会是什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.65,0:15:10.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是什么呢 看来像是什么的残骸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.23,0:15:15.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.96,0:15:17.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,长嘴硬鳞鱼号
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.23,0:15:23.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,或许石像鬼就在里头
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.44,0:15:26.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 要是他真在附近 就大事不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.54,0:15:28.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,里头没人在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.75,0:15:36.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它跟鹦鹉螺号对战过吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.92,0:15:38.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,应该是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.38,0:15:42.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为应该只有鹦鹉螺号 才有办法打倒长嘴硬鳞鱼号
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.59,0:15:46.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉 不可以离开我们 太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.46,0:15:48.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.36,0:15:49.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,走吧 大王
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.80,0:15:50.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.70,0:15:52.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.63,0:15:56.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看它锈蚀成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.20,0:15:58.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,应该已经有一个月以上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.80,0:16:00.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再说 如果还有幸存者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.61,0:16:02.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就不会留下那么多罐头
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.04,0:16:05.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,应该都到某个城镇去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.98,0:16:10.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么…这附近应该有城镇是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.71,0:16:42.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.22,0:16:44.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了？强
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.88,0:16:47.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这里是刚才的沙滩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.79,0:16:49.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.72,0:16:51.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.19,0:16:53.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀 真讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.19,0:16:53.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.86,0:16:57.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚 强
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.80,0:17:00.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我又捡到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.40,0:17:03.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也就是说…\N也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.47,0:17:05.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这里…\N这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.80,0:17:08.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是座岛！\N是座岛！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.88,0:17:14.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们有遇到什么人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.15,0:17:18.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有发现人烟吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.69,0:17:26.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也就是说…\N也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.76,0:17:29.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是座无人岛！\N这是座无人岛！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.85,0:17:52.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么我总是被不幸缠身呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.82,0:17:55.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想去的地方可是非洲耶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.55,0:17:58.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再怎么样都不该跑来无人岛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.02,0:18:02.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,姑丈一定很担心我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.79,0:18:05.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可能认为我已经死了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.43,0:18:09.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,葛兰迪丝他们 也不知道飞到哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.47,0:18:13.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,结果那时候 他们是开葛兰坦逃了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.87,0:18:16.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那时候的推进器 是做什么用的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.84,0:18:18.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是韩森的发明吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.21,0:18:22.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们果然是坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.15,0:18:24.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不该对他们好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.52,0:18:26.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好羡慕韩森喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.59,0:18:30.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也好想制作出 具有独创性的发明
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.66,0:18:35.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,应该有比发明更要紧的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.87,0:18:45.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.54,0:18:47.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,天就快黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.81,0:18:50.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,趁天色还亮的时候 得快点去拿粮食过来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.61,0:18:56.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好…好远…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.82,0:19:03.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们连饭都没得吃是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.82,0:19:06.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对了 让玛莉与大王…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.79,0:19:09.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有船！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.66,0:19:13.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那边 那边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.17,0:19:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哪边？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.37,0:19:15.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.30,0:19:18.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂\N喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.51,0:19:22.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.78,0:19:28.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.15,0:19:31.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没办法 强
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.32,0:19:33.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,根本传不到那么远
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.69,0:19:36.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行啦 不能那么轻易放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.19,0:19:37.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你看着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.45,0:20:10.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这下没救了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.80,0:20:22.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.97,0:20:23.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.67,0:20:29.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.04,0:20:31.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.41,0:20:34.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鹦鹉螺号的紧急存粮吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.18,0:20:35.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你怎么会有这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.18,0:20:37.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我拿来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.05,0:20:40.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么拿来的？\N怎么拿来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.59,0:20:41.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用走的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.85,0:20:43.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用走的？\N用走的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.49,0:20:49.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们看 用走的就可以到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.03,0:20:52.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原来潮水退了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.80,0:20:54.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.74,0:21:02.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.47,0:21:03.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.84,0:21:06.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没有开罐头的工具
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.51,0:21:08.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.25,0:21:11.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,反正也没有我能吃的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.48,0:21:14.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么办 这样会饿死的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.39,0:21:15.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.49,0:21:17.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王说它会开
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.66,0:21:19.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么开？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.85,0:21:45.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王 这样会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.59,0:21:54.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.59,0:21:56.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你怎么可以自己吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.83,0:22:02.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.57,0:22:05.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王刚刚吃过 所以不用吃了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.54,0:22:07.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明天也要麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.78,0:22:15.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个你应该可以吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.01,0:22:17.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.28,0:22:21.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,炸过的马铃薯薄片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.86,0:22:26.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.49,0:22:28.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.93,0:22:29.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.23,0:22:33.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 它的味道跟肉一样耶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.70,0:22:34.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.83,0:22:38.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是将马铃薯切成薄片 炸过之后再干燥的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.40,0:22:40.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你根本只是挑食嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.77,0:22:42.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.21,0:22:45.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,挑食 挑食
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.08,0:22:46.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你管我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.96,0:23:05.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别踩到喔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.63,0:23:07.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.50,0:23:12.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我在藉由星星的位置 判断这座岛大概在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.84,0:23:16.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.48,0:23:23.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.48,0:23:25.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用不着去查那些事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.32,0:23:27.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.45,0:23:31.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这座岛上就只有我们
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.69,0:23:34.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没有其他坏人和讨厌的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.56,0:23:39.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要能跟玛莉、大王在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.50,0:23:41.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我可以一辈子都待在这座岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.67,0:23:43.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.21,0:23:49.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那我呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.58,0:23:53.70,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,待续
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.71,0:24:02.61,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,该怎么应付心中的焦急才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.68,0:24:07.74,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就要看不清远方的梦想了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.82,0:24:12.12,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我喃喃自语 仰望星空
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.19,0:24:21.00,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,与你的约定耀眼闪烁着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.07,0:24:31.10,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Try 安慰的话语 是传达不到内心的风
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.18,0:24:40.02,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然背负的不安逐渐膨胀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.09,0:24:44.18,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但这是我自己的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.26,0:24:48.89,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一个人应该也不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.96,0:24:57.60,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即使跌倒或感到迷惘 仍然有明天
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.45,0:25:09.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强、玛莉、大王
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.82,0:25:12.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,思考了一整晚之后 我重生了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.82,0:25:13.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.89,0:25:14.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不会再愁眉不展
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.05,0:25:16.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也不会再乱发脾气
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.32,0:25:18.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我已经不是 以前那个娜蒂亚了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.26,0:25:22.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对 我已经重生为 南方岛屿的娜蒂亚了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.30,0:25:23.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.93,0:25:27.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海底两万里 下一回 『林肯岛』
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.00,0:25:28.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要看喔\N要看喔
